INSERT INTO `pages` VALUES (1,'Balance Transfer',NULL,2,12,1,12,'<p>The following balance transfer credit card offers from our partners are designed to help people consolidate their credit card debt onto one card, thus saving money on interest charges. Some of the credit card offers below even feature a low introductory 0% APR interest rate on credit card balance transfers.</p>\n','Looking to save with a balance transfer? Compare the best offers from all major issuers, including 0% APR for up to 18 months.','Balance Transfer Credit Cards, credit card, best, 0%, low apr, low interest, online, credit card applications, CreditCards.com','balance-transfer',1,NULL,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2016-01-04 07:07:54'),(2,'Cash Back',NULL,2,15,1,13,'<p>The following cash back credit cards from our partners feature reward programs that offer cash back or rebate incentives. A Cash Back Credit Card rewards you for using them with cash back incentives and rebate programs. Credit cards with cash rebates and incentives usually require a good to excellent credit rating for approval.</p>\n','You could be earning more cash back; up to 5% in select categories and sign-up bonuses up to $200. Browse the best cash back offers from leading banks.','Cash Back Credit Cards, credit card, cash back credit card, Credit Cards, cash back, credit card rewards programs, apply, online, credit card application, creditcards, rebate','cash-back',1,NULL,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2016-01-04 07:08:16'),(3,'Low Interest',NULL,2,11,1,13,'<p>The following Low Interest Credit Cards from our partners feature either a low fixed rate APR or a low introductory APR. Apply for the credit card of your choice by filling out a secure online application.</p>\n','Low Interest Credit Cards at CreditCards.com featuring low interest rate and 0% apr credit cards. Apply today with an on line secure low interest credit card application.','low interest credit cards, credit card, creditcard, 0%, low apr, apply, online, rate, credit card applications, application','low-interest',1,NULL,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2016-01-01 08:34:26'),(4,'Homepage',NULL,1,1,4,0,'','Find the best credit card deals by comparing a variety of offers for balance transfers, rewards, low interest, and more. Apply online at CreditCards.com.','credit cards, credit card, credit, creditcards, visa, offers, search, compare, apply, mastercard, low interest, student, instant approval, balance transfer, reward, business, cash back','index',1,NULL,'2016-01-01 04:06:31','2016-01-01 08:36:33'),(5,'0% APR',NULL,2,1477,1,13,'<p>The primary benefit of a 0% APR credit card is the introductory 0% APR interest rate. This rate is available anywhere from 6 to 18 months or more from when the credit card account is opened. Depending on the card offer, it will be applied to new purchases, balance transfers or both. Compare 0% credit cards from our partners and apply online.</p>\n','0% APR credit cards may be a good financial decision for you. Choose from a wide variety of 0% APR credit cards at CreditCards.com.','0% APR credit cards, 0% credit cards, zero APR, 0% APR, credit cards','0-apr-credit-cards',0,NULL,'2016-01-01 08:02:28','2016-01-04 03:54:12'),(6,'No Annual Fee',NULL,2,2005,1,13,'<p>The following cards from our partners save you money by not charging an annual fee. Some of the cards listed below waive the annual fee for the first year, but may charge a fee for subsequent years. Some even offer rewards and low interest rates.</p>\n','No annual fee credit cards offer both savings and may come with additional benefits such as reward points, cash back, hotel stays or balance transfer discounts.','no annual fee credit cards, zero fee, apply for no fee credit card, 0 fee credit card, compare','no-annual-fee',1,NULL,'2016-01-01 08:07:53','2016-01-01 08:07:53'),(7,'No Foreign Transaction Fee',NULL,2,2022,1,13,'<p>The following cards save you money when you travel outside the United States by not charging a foreign transaction fee. These cards are attractive to cardholders who travel overseas, and would like to have the convenience of using a credit card for their purchases. Compare cards with no international transaction fees from our partners below.</p>\n','International travelers can compare credit cards that offer 0% foreign transaction fees.  Save money while on your trip abroad.','no foreign transaction fee credit cards, zero foreign fee, apply for no foreign fee credit card, 0 fee travel cards, compare','no-foreign-transaction-fee',1,NULL,'2016-01-01 08:09:14','2016-01-01 08:09:14'),(8,'Travel and Airline',NULL,2,16,1,13,'<p>The following travel credit cards from our partners offer airline or hotel rewards. You can earn frequent flyer miles or rewards points when you travel or when you spend. The frequent flyer miles or rewards points can be redeemed for airline discounts or free nights at participating hotels. If you are a frequent flyer or travel a lot, an airline or travel credit card could help save you money.</p>\n','Want to earn free flights and nights? Compare the best travel reward offers from major banks, airlines, and hotels. Sign-up bonuses up to 60,000 points.','Airline Credit Cards, frequent flyer credit cards, airline credit card, visa, signature card, Credit Cards, best, online, mileage applications, application','airline-miles',1,NULL,'2016-01-01 08:10:53','2016-01-01 08:10:53'),(9,'Hotel Cards',NULL,2,2314,1,13,'<p>Are you looking for a hotel card? From the budget-minded to the luxury traveler, the right credit card can enhance your travel experience. The following hotel cards from our partners offer a variety of benefits at some of your favorite hotels including complimentary stays, membership status, and room upgrades. If convenience is top priority when you travel, and you aren&#39;t loyal to one hotel chain, check out some of the flexible rewards cards listed below instead. Flexible rewards cards allow you to redeem points for hotel travel expenses, regardless of the hotel brand.</p>\n','Earn free nights and elite status with the right hotel credit card. Check the latest offers and signup bonuses from all major hotel chains and banks.','hotel credit cards, hotels credit cards, hotel rewards credit cards, hotel loyalty credit cards, hotel chain credit cards, hotel travel credit cards','hotel-cards',1,NULL,'2016-01-01 08:12:17','2016-01-02 05:13:56'),(10,'Credit Cards with EMV',NULL,2,2116,1,13,'<p>The following cards from our partners contain EMV chip technology (also referred to as smart chips). These cards offer an enhanced security against counterfeiting or cloning. &quot;Chip and signature&quot; is becoming the standard authorization process in the US. However, this standard is different than the &quot;Chip and PIN&quot; standard used in much of the rest of the world. Still, many frequent travelers find these cards more easily accepted overseas.</p>\n','Stay secure with an EMV chip credit card. Compare cards that include the latest Chip & Signature technology; a must for international travelers.','smart chip credit cards, chip and signature, chip and PIN credit cards, smart chip technology, EMV smart card technology, chip and pin credit cards usa','smart-emv-chip',1,NULL,'2016-01-01 08:14:06','2016-01-01 08:14:06'),(11,'Reward',NULL,2,14,1,13,'<p>The following reward credit cards from our partners feature either cash back or rewards programs. Rewards Program Credit Cards &quot;reward&quot; you for using them with cash back incentives and rebate programs.</p>\n','Want great credit card rewards?  Choose among the numerous offers available at CreditCards.com','Reward Credit Cards, credit card, reward credit cards, credit card, Credit Cards, cash back, credit card rewards programs, apply, online, credit card application, applications, rebate','reward',1,NULL,'2016-01-01 08:16:07','2016-01-01 08:16:07'),(13,'Points',NULL,2,77,1,13,'<p>The following Points Reward credit cards from our partners feature the ability to earn reward points for card purchases. Reward points can then be redeemed for a variety of items, including merchandise, gift cards or cash back. Apply today for the Points Reward credit card of your choice by completing a secure online application.</p>\n','Points Rewards Credit Cards - Search, Compare, Apply, Save at CreditCards.com. Apply online and start earning rebates with a secure credit card application.','Points Rewards Credit Cards, credit card, reward credit cards, Credit Cards, cash back','points',1,NULL,'2016-01-01 08:39:13','2016-01-01 08:39:13'),(14,'Gas Cards',NULL,2,79,1,13,'<p>The following Gas Rebate credit cards from our partners allow consumers to earn higher cash back rebates for gas purchases along with 1% on all other purchases. With Gas Rebate credit cards you can reduce the high cost of driving with your everyday credit card spending. Apply for the gas card of your choice today by completing a secure online application.</p>\n','Frequent driver? CreditCards.com has numerous offers on gas credit cards that give rebates on gas purchases.','Gas Cards, credit card, reward credit cards, Credit Cards, cash back','gas-cards',1,NULL,'2016-01-01 08:40:31','2016-01-02 03:57:51'),(15,'Excellent Credit',NULL,2,76,1,13,'<p>The following Credit Cards are for People with Excellent Credit. Compare offers from our partners side by side and apply online for the card that is right for you. Apply for the Excellent Credit card of your choice by completing a secure online application.</p>\n','Credit cards for People with Excellent Credit - compare credit card offers and apply online at CreditCards.com. Choose from both secured and unsecured credit card offers below.','credit cards Excellent Credit, Credit Card Offers for People with Excellent Credit, credit cards, Excellent Credit card, credit card,  best, no credit, pre paid, visa, secured, apply, online, applications, application, unsecured','excellent-credit',1,NULL,'2016-01-01 08:43:32','2016-01-01 08:43:32'),(16,'Good Credit',NULL,2,75,1,13,'<p>The following Credit Cards are for People with Good Credit. Compare offers side by side and apply online for the card that is right for you. Apply for the Good Credit credit card of your choice by completing a secure online application.</p>\n','Have good credit? Compare credit cards at CreditCards.com to get the best deal for you.','credit cards Good Credit, Credit Card Offers for People with Good Credit, credit cards, Good Credit credit card, credit card,  best, no credit, pre paid, visa, secured, apply, online, applications, application, unsecured','good-credit',1,NULL,'2016-01-01 08:45:32','2016-01-01 08:45:32'),(17,'Fair Credit',NULL,2,74,1,13,'<p>The following Credit Cards and Prepaid Debit Cards are for People with Fair Credit. Compare offers side by side and apply online for the card that is right for you. Apply for the Fair Credit credit card or prepaid debit card of your choice by completing a secure online application.</p>\n','Credit cards for People with Fair Credit - compare credit card offers and apply online at CreditCards.com. Choose from both secured and unsecured credit card offers below.','credit cards fair credit, Credit Card Offers for People with Fair Credit, credit cards, fair credit credit card, credit card,  best, no credit, pre paid, visa, secured, apply, online, applications, application, unsecured','fair-credit',1,NULL,'2016-01-01 08:47:57','2016-01-01 08:47:57'),(18,'Credit Cards for Limited or No Credit History',NULL,2,1077,1,13,'<p>The following Credit Cards and Prepaid Debit Cards are for people with limited or no credit history. Compare offers side by side and apply online for the card that is right for you.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"/credit-card-news/credit-card-law-interactive-1282.php\">Federal laws impose restrictions on issuing credit cards to individuals under 21 unless the applicant has the independent ability to repay debt or has a co-signer over the age of 21 who agrees to accept joint liability for the account. </a></p>\n','Compare credit cards for people with no credit history and apply online at CreditCards.com.','credit cards no credit History, Credit Card Offers for people with limited or no credit history, credit cards, no credit History credit card, credit card,  best, no credit, pre paid, visa, secured, apply, online, applications, application, unsecured','no-credit-history',1,NULL,'2016-01-01 08:52:10','2016-01-01 08:52:10'),(19,'Debit Cards & Prepaid Cards',NULL,2,19,1,13,'<p>The following Debit cards and Prepaid cards from our partners can help you control your spending. If you tend to overspend or would like to control your spending then a debit card or a prepaid card could be a good card for you. Debit cards &amp; prepaid cards are not credit cards.</p>\n','Prepaid cards and debit cards can help your control your spending. Compare cards and apply online at CreditCards.com','Prepaid Debit Cards & Prepaid Credit Card Offers, prepaid cards, prepaid card, debit cards, prepaid debit cards, debit card, secured credit card, credit card, best, no credit, pre paid, bad credit, student, secured, mastercard, ecount, online, application','prepaid',1,NULL,'2016-01-01 12:01:43','2016-01-01 12:01:43'),(20,'Secured Credit Card Options and Offers',NULL,2,1768,1,13,'<p>Secured credit cards can help establish or rebuild your credit history. Unlike prepaid cards, secured credit cards give you a credit line, and your payment activity will be reported to the major credit bureaus. <b>Please note: before any secured card can be activated, it MUST be funded with a security deposit equal to the credit line</b>.</p>\n','New to credit cards? Rebuilding after a major event? A secured credit card may be the best option for you. Compare secured credit cards at Creditcards.com and re-establish or establish solid credit worthiness.','secured credit card, secured credit cards, credit cards, credit card, establish credit, re-establish credit','secured-credit-card',1,NULL,'2016-01-01 12:03:35','2016-01-01 12:03:35'),(21,'Top 10 Best Credit Cards',NULL,4,37,2,13,'<p>Below is a list of this month&#39;s top 10 featured credit card offers. To see more offers from a category, simply follow the link. Finding a great credit card deal is as easy as 1,2,3...</p>\n','Our picks for the 10 best credit card offers and deals for January, 2016, including the top cash back, balance transfer and reward credit cards.','best credit card deals, offers, 2016, promotions, credit card, creditcard, 0%, APR, low apr, balance transfer, cash back, reward, frequent flyer','top-credit-cards',1,NULL,'2016-01-01 12:06:52','2016-01-01 12:08:03'),(22,'Personal Loans',NULL,2,2372,1,13,'<p>Are you looking for credit card alternatives?&nbsp; We&rsquo;ve compiled a list of emergency loans and peer-to-peer lending options to help you with your search. Emergency loan options can help deal with short-term financial emergencies, while peer-to-peer lending options can give borrowers access to funds for a variety of purposes, often at lower interest rates than traditional credit cards.</p>\n','Find the personal loan thatâ€™s right for you. Compare rates on person to person loans, emergency loans and other personal loans at Creditcards.com','personal loans, personal loan, person to person lending, emergency loans, social lending','personal-loans',1,NULL,'2016-01-01 12:10:49','2016-01-01 12:10:49');
